      </h3>
      <p>
        “<a href='/word_detail.php?id=398' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yǒu', 'is / are / to have')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">有</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=894' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zì', 'letter / symbol / character')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">字</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=6711' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jù', 'sentence / clause / phrase')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">句</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=650' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yǐ', 'so as to')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">以</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9256' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '動詞 dòngcí', 'verb')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=398' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yǒu', 'is / are / to have')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">有</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9255' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '充當 chōngdāng', 'to serve as')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">充当</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9250' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '謂語 wèiyǔ', 'predicate')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">谓语</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=986' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jīběn', 'basic / fundamental')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">基本</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=6171' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'géshì', 'form / specification / format')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">格式</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a>：<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9249' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '主語 zhǔyǔ', 'subject')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">主语</a> ＋ “<a href='/word_detail.php?id=398' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yǒu', 'is / are / to have')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">有</a>” ＋　<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9260' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '賓語 bīnyǔ', 'object')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">宾语</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2846' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bǐrú', 'for example / for instance / such as')" 
